<section id="contact">
  <div class="neon-box-container">
    <div class="neon-box">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Contact me
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-8 lg:mb-16 font-light text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:text-xl">
        Passionate web developer in training, eager to bring your ideas to life. <br> 
        I offer fresh perspectives and a commitment to quality work.<br> 
        I prioritize user experience, crafting intuitive and visually appealing websites. <br> 
        Available for internships, and web development opportunities.<br> 
        Contact me today!
      </p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <button type="submit" class=" w-full py-3 px-5 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg bg-primary-700 hover:bg-primary-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-primary-300 dark:bg-primary-600 dark:hover:bg-primary-700 dark:focus:ring-primary-800"><a href="mailto:lorenzo.zanuso@epitech.eu?subject=Mail de notre site Web ">Send email</a></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
